{"tid":2277460,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解呢個世界得PUSH UP BRA冇PUSH UP底褲?","createTime":"2020-11-08T13:08:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T07:49:34.000Z","uid":124841,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"41587b6f437a535137a957e68d0684ad2a8d354e","tid":2277460,"uid":124841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"港女鬼影變幻球係人都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本push up bra就係一種增強女性自信既產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇落有個cup手波 但一除bra就平過機場<br />\n但偏偏就成日用個bra硬唧個波仔出黎欺騙男性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人就唔同 未扯之前其實著泳褲/底褲個陣 好難會見到一大抽野(除非你係黑人或者天賦異稟)<br />\n變相就減少左男人既吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋男人扯左同未扯真係差太遠<br />\n好似本人未扯大概3cm到 但扯左可以去到8-9cm 唔講係大抽 但係香港應該都算係中上size<br />\n不過成日著泳褲個種就俾d女指住黎笑 我又唔想扯起黎嚇鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得市面上應該推出d push up底褲 等我地男人都可以自信咁出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個應該會係劃時代發明黎"},{"pid":"823cb48cc503a31a431ef4f15fb1e171f66d7968","tid":2277460,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:09:35.000Z","msg":"Aa9帶假撈"},{"pid":"d068d378f053b7020f66c0854036da1ae8955eb2","tid":2277460,"uid":145557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:14:24.000Z","msg":"我扯完有10cm 樓主得9cm係咪女人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22077c98737248878392306a44914c8186fe9325","tid":2277460,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T13:16:29.000Z","msg":"9cm CLS"},{"pid":"795f500